.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[181,545,1036,1063]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Collectés en 1932 par F. Keiser.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1071,1097]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Cette espèce ne se rencontre qu’à</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1104,1131]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
très haute altitude (
<bibRefCitation author="Speight M. C. D." box="[369,520,1104,1131]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" refId="ref3524" refString="Speight M. C. D. 2020. Species accounts of European Syrphidae (Diptera), Vol. 104. Syrph the Net Publications, Dublin, 314 pp." type="book" year="2020">Speight 2020</bibRefCitation>
) et
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1138,1165]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">jusqu’à présent n’était connue que</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1173,1199]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">du Nord de l’Italie, très proche de la</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1207,1233]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
<collectingCountry box="[151,223,1207,1233]" name="Switzerland" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Suisse</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Nielsen T. R." box="[237,391,1207,1233]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" pagination="1 - 30" refId="ref3103" refString="Nielsen T. R. 2004. European species of the Platycheirus ambiguus group (Diptera, Syrphidae), with description of new species. Volucella 7: 1 - 30." type="journal article" year="2004">Nielsen 2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielsen T. R." box="[401,458,1207,1233]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" pagination="57 - 75" refId="ref3136" refString="Nielsen T. R. 2014. Synopsis of the Platycheirus ambiguus species group (Diptera, Syrphidae), with description of Platycheirus arnei sp. n. and a preliminary key to the species. Norwegian Journal of Entomology 61: 57 - 75." type="journal article" year="2014">2014</bibRefCitation>
). Sa pré-
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1241,1267]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">sence était donc supposée et atten-</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1275,1301]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
due en 
<collectingCountry box="[242,314,1275,1301]" name="Switzerland" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Suisse</collectingCountry>
sur les sommets de
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1309,1335]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
plus de 
<quantity box="[240,325,1309,1335]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" unit="m" value="3000.0">3000 m</quantity>
d’altitude et les don-
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1343,1369]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">nées découvertes dans les musées</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,555,1377,1403]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">laissent supposer qu’on la trouve</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1411,1437]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
aussi en 
<collectingCountry box="[250,354,1411,1437]" name="Austria" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">Autriche</collectingCountry>
, du moins proche
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,555,1445,1471]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">du Piz Terza (aussi appelé Urtiola</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,555,1479,1506]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">ou Urtirola-Spitze). Sa description</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,555,1513,1539]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">ne date que de 2004 et cette espèce</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,556,1547,1573]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">était auparavant confondue avec</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,798,1676]" box="[151,558,1581,1607]" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">
l’espèce 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fallen, 1817)" baseAuthorityName="Fallen" baseAuthorityYear="1817" box="[248,554,1581,1607]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Platycheirus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ambiguus">
<emphasis box="[248,389,1581,1607]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="125">P. ambiguus</emphasis>
(Fallén, 1817)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
